content: I think I'll try Poshmark for selling my old college t-shirts. I've heard good things about it, and it seems easy to use. Do you know if I can sell my light blue denim shirt from Gap on Poshmark as well? It's in good condition, but it's a bit too tight for me, so I'm thinking of getting rid of it. And, by the way, I wore my new black jeans from Levi's last weekend, and they're really comfortable. I've worn them four times so far, and they still look great.
